WEBVTT

00:10:58.080 --> 00:11:01.936
and we ran a trial there
in 120 birth centers.

00:11:01.960 --> 00:11:05.936
In Uttar Pradesh,
in India's largest state.

00:11:05.960 --> 00:11:10.976
Half of the centers
basically we just observed,

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:13.936
but the other half
got visits from coaches.

00:11:13.960 --> 00:11:17.736
We trained an army
of doctors and nurses like this one

00:11:17.760 --> 00:11:22.096
who learned to observe the care
and also the managers

00:11:22.120 --> 00:11:24.416
and then help them
build on their strengths

00:11:24.440 --> 00:11:26.080
and address their weaknesses.

00:11:26.880 --> 00:11:29.936
One of the skills for example
they had to work on with people --

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:32.016
turned out to be
fundamentally important --